<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Golang on Rogee's 备忘录</title><link>http://notes.711xd.com/tags/golang/</link><description>Recent content in Golang on Rogee's 备忘录</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><copyright>Rogee</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Nov 2021 16:28:40 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="http://notes.711xd.com/tags/golang/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>golang float32/64与[]byte互转</title><link>http://notes.711xd.com/post/golang-float-byte-convert/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Nov 2021 16:28:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://notes.711xd.com/post/golang-float-byte-convert/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
